<DOC><DOCNO>WSJ900928-0166</DOCNO><DOCID>900928-0166.</DOCID><HL>   Howtek, Adobe Systems in Pact</HL><DATE>09/28/90</DATE><SO>WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION</SO><CO>   HTK ADBE</CO><IN>COMPUTERS AND INFORMATION TECHNOLOGY (CPR)SOFTWARE (SOF)</IN><LP>   HUDSON, N.H. -- Howtek Inc. said it signed an agreementwith Adobe Systems Inc. to combine Howtek's Personal Colorscanner with Adobe's Photoshop Limited Edition, a specialversion of Adobe's Photoshop software.   Howtek said the combination of the two products will allowpersonal computers to use color for such applications asbusiness graphics, presentations and color desktoppublishing.</LP><TEXT>   The product will be available for shipment by the end ofOctober and will retail for about $2,595.   Howtek makes computer products for the color graphicsmarket. Adobe is a software concern based in Palo Alto,Calif.</TEXT></DOC>